  <span class="help-text">Pink/Purple Rings: Teleporters</span>
  <span class="help-text">Blue Tiles: Ice (less friction)</span>
  <span class="help-text">Green Tiles: Boost pads</span>
  <span class="help-text">Orange Walls: Moving walls (oscillate!)</span>
  <span class="help-text">Green Pads: Gravity switch (reverses tilt!)</span>
  <span class="help-section">Power-Ups</span>
  <span class="help-text">Blue Sphere: Shield (survive one fall)</span>
  <span class="help-text">Gold Hex: Magnet (attract gems)</span>
  <span class="help-text">Purple Knot: Slow-Mo (precision)</span>
  <span class="help-section">Star Rating</span>
  <span class="help-text">★ Complete | ★★ Under par | ★★★ Par + all gems</span>
